org.sakaiproject.util

Class DbResourceBundle

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.ResourceBundle
      • org.sakaiproject.util.DbResourceBundle

  • public class DbResourceBundle
extends ResourceBundle
    An extension of ResourceBundle which gets the bundle data in the normal way and then consults with the MessageBundleService for addition data. Any values returned by the MessageBundleService will override values returned from the normal ResourceBundle. Also provides a method to index new bundle data by interacting with the MessageBundleService to do the real work. Created by IntelliJ IDEA.
